      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) used as primary comparison metric. CFD predictions compared against experimental NIH measurements across all 5 operating points. Mean absolute error is 8.2%, maximum error 14.7%, both within the defined acceptance band of 20%. Statistical comparison using Bland-Altman analysis confirms no systematic bias. Achieved level exceeds requirement."
