      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is geometrically representative of the Class II CPB device under assessment. Blood analogue fluid (glycerol-water mixture with matched viscosity at 37°C) used in experiments. Operating conditions span the full CPB clinical envelope. Validation activities are judged sufficiently relevant to the COU."
