      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, numerical solver error beyond code verification is not required to be formally assessed provided the solver is a validated commercial code.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent is a validated commercial CFD solver. Formal iterative convergence monitoring is performed (residuals < 1e-6), and solver error is implicitly bounded by code verification activities. Formal separate assessment of numerical solver error is not required at MRL 2 and is scoped out of this assessment."
